Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.66,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:08.36,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:13.53,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:18.67,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:31.42,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:39.86,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:51.74,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:55.01,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.78,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:01:02.65,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:08.13,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:17.44,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:32.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Use it like that to kill the criminals\Nwho are broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:36.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then, you can use the notebook\Nhowever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:37.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If everything goes according\Nto Light Yagami's plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this is sure to save Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:48.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good deal\Nfor both of us, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:53.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I guess as you would say...\Nit's good business.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:01.39,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,0)}Fiftieth Day in Confinement
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:01.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,388)}Mr. Yagami, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:05.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for you\Nto stay there like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:10.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been over a month since Kira\Nstarted to kill criminals again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:14.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure that my son isn't Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:19.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, all that's left is for you to be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:23.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I get out when my son does...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:26.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief sure is stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:30.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:34.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm all right, but...Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:38.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,criminals have stopped dying\Nsince I've been confined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:41.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's highly likely that Kira\Nis someone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:43.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who knows about my situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:45.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- If we go with this line of reasoning...\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:48.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Criminals are not dying\Nbecause you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must\NI say it until you'll understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:57.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira should know that killings\Nhave begun again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like he knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is cruel, Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:05.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't told Light that\Ncriminals are being killed again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:08.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:09.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're tired,\Nbut are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There'd be something\Nwrong with me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if I was all right after\Nall these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:20.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go...\NI want to see Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:28.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:30.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like all three\Nof them are at their limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, why are you\Nstill confining Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:39.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should let him go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:41.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, the Chief\Nwill come out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Criminals are still being killed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:46.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even though Misa and Light aren't\Nable to obtain any information.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We know at least that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:50.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:54.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All we know is that Amane harbors an\Nunnaturally strong love for Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:59.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...sorry, but I think\Nthat you're doing this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:04.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because you don't want to admit\Nthat you were wrong about Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:05.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:11.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As Light has said, Kira's killed\NLind L.Tailor and the FBI agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:14.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira could kill under surveillance and\Nwithout obtaining information,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:17.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then he wouldn't have\Nneeded to kill Tailor and the FBI agents!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard we investigate,\Nhe can't be traced.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira doesn't kill without a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You even said so yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he could kill in these circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:32.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he shouldn't have had a problem\Nwith leaving those FBI agents alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:35.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been fifty days...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:38.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to be doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:42.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, we should be thinking\Nof ways to catch the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:03.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:08.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you return to task force\Nheadquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:11.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to hear my theory\Non what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:15.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, I want to talk to you\Nas Light's Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:18.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:41.11,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,0)}Three days later
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:45.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that you would\Nbe an old man, Mister Stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a stalker. I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:49.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:51.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:55.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that I was being arrested\Nfor being the Second Kira or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:57.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:02.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way the police would\Ntie me up in such a fetish-like way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:05.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, isn't it strange that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:07.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my hands and feet are restrained even\Nthough you're going to let me go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Light!\N- Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:25.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dying to see you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Dad-?\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I called your dad a stalker and\Nother rude things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:33.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Misa Amane.\NI'm currently going out with Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave it to you, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NHurry up and get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:52.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally cleared\Nand are free to go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:53.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are now...\Nbeing taken to your execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:03.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I volunteered to escort you\Nto the execution site,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:06.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,secretly built in\Nan underground facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Our execution?\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- What are you talking about, Dad?\N- This is a joke, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L has decided that Light Yagami\Nis Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:14.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and Misa Amane is\Nthe Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:19.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He decided that if you were executed,\Nthe killings would stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't the killings stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're still continuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:27.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuing?\NThat's not what he told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:31.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L was trying to get\Na confession out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:39.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L's suggestion that the killings\Nwould stop if you two were eliminated...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was immediately accepted\Nby all the top officials of the UN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Japanese government.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:47.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will be erased,\Nhidden from the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:51.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy.\NWait, Dad, I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your own son!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:59.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not my decision, it's L's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:04.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He has solved many difficult cases\Nin the past and never been wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:09.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...do you trust L\Nmore than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L says that if the killings don't stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:16.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then he'll take responsibility\Nand end his own life...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L... What are you thinking-?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:22.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that from\Nthe material investigation up to now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:24.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this may seem like\Nthe only logical answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:29.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did L come to this conclusion-?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:30.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like L at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:37.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L's always used hard evidence\Nin all of his cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he planning to end it like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:01.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:03.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring us out to\Nthe middle of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:04.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:07.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to let us go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody will see us here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:16.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to bring you here\Ninstead of the execution site.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill you here\Nand then kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's crazy!\N- Stop it already! You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill your child and then yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:33.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to die, then why don't\Nyou just die by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do this, then you'll be\Nno different from Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:36.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm different from Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:41.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a responsibility as a parent\Nand as the Detective Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, Misa's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:46.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we die here,\Nwe'll never find out the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:48.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be better if we ran away-!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:49.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late, Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you'll be executed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:54.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least this way...it'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by my own hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop Dad! I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die here,\Nwe all fall into Kira's trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:07.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane... I'm going to die here\Nwith my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:14.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police will probably\Nfind this car soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:17.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be executed at\Nthe original site.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:26.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...from one murderer to another,\NI'll see you in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:33.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:52.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...from one murderer to another,\NI'll see you in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:14.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A blank-?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:24.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness?\NWhat are you doing, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the only way to\Nfree you from confinement...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But please understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:36.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did this because I believe\Nthat you're not Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you watching, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:41.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did as you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:43.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and as you can see,\NI'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:46.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was a convincing performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:52.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Amane were the Second Kira,\Nwho can kill just by knowing a person's face,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:56.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then she would have killed you\Nbefore you fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:59.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if Light were Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:03.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Kira I know would even kill\Nhis parents if he was in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In Light's case, I cannot deny\Nthe possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that he may have discovered\Nit was all an act halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:13.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But as I promised,\NI will end their confinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:15.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also as promised,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:18.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even though she insists that\Nthose tapes where just occult videos,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:22.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have physical evidence and\Na confession that she sent the Kira videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:23.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So Misa Amane will remain\Nunder surveillance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until Kira is caught and\Nhis case is resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?\NDo you still suspect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:32.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you get to return\Nto your everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:35.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:38.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you can think of the surveillance\Nas police protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:42.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Since I'm not the Second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:44.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should think of it like\NI have some bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:51.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will arrange things so that\Nyou and I will be together 24 hours a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:54.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,working on the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:05.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Ryuzaki.\NLet's catch Kira together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm looking forward\Nto working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:15.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really necessary Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:18.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing this\Nbecause I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:22.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is what you meant by being\Ntogether with him 24 hours a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:24.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda gross for two men\Nto be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, is that what you're into?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:29.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'm not doing\Nthis because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:32.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Light belongs to Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:33.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're together with him\N24 hours a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then when will I have the time\Nto go on dates with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:39.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dates will be with the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:42.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you telling me we\Nhave to kiss in front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:46.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling you to do anything.\NBut I will be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a pervert, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, please silence Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:54.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, don't be selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were definitely\Nthe one who sent the tapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:01.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,just be grateful that you're allowed\Nas much freedom as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:06.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your girlfriend, aren't l?\NDon't you trust your own lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:10.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Girlfriend? You said you fell in love\Nwith me at first sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:12.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and now you're always\Nforcing yourself on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:17.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So then you took advantage\Nof that fact and kissed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:20.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid-!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About this "love at first sight" thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:26.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened in Aoyama\Non May 22, didn't it, Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you go to Aoyama\Non that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I just happened\Nto go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:35.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:38.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really remember how\NI felt that day or what I wore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it so wrong for me to be\Nhanging out in Aoyama without a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So when you came back from Aoyama,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you were in love with Light\Nand knew his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:48.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know\Nhow you knew his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:56.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how would you feel\Nif Light was Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? If Light was Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:00.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:03.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be wonderful-!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been grateful to Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:09.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for punishing the man\Nwho murdered my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:13.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light were Kira, I'd love him more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I love him so much already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about Kira, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd love him even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel afraid at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:24.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's supposing if Light is Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:26.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:28.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of those people\Nwho accept Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd think of ways I could help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd probably get in his way\Nrather than help him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:39.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:42.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no mistake that\Nyou are the Second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:47.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's so clear-cut that\NI don't want to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:51.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't believe it,\Nbecause I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:54.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you'll remain under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:58.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you go out, contact us using\Nthis room's extension.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:00.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on for private\Nand work-related affairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Matsuda will accompany you\Nas your manager, Matsui.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already paid off your agency
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- to agree to this.\N- Hey there, I'm Matsui.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:11.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't told the police,\Nso be sure not to give yourself away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:14.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This old man's gonna be my manager?\NHow awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!\NWhat's wrong with me, Misa-Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:24.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out with all this dating,\Nkissing, and Misa-Misa talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Kira case! Understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:29.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:34.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry. I know we're serious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane, go to your room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:38.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:41.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No questions, c'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:44.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Let's go on a date,\Neven if it's the three of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, are you serious about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... As I said earlier,\Nit's one-sided...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:56.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then could you act as\Nif you're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:59.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that Amane's connected\Nwith the Second Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from the video incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:03.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And also from the way she loves you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asking me to become\Nintimate with her
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can find out information\Nabout the Second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I think you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:15.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we could get clues to solve\Nthis case from Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I released both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:20.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's for the Kira case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:28.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never use\Na woman's feelings like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:31.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, you need to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:36.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, taking advantage of\Nanother person's feelings is unforgivable,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:38.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the most despicable thing\Na person can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:40.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only assume that\Nhis personality has changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really an act?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:50.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it sounds like Amane\Nwas being controlled by Kira, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Yagami as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:55.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:58.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it would be helpful if\Nyou could make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:05.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she doesn't leak any information\Nabout the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:12.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, can't we change this system\Nof changing hotels every few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:16.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I've also been thinking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:17.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's why...\N- Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:19.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Construction started immediately after...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:21.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my first meeting with Mr. Yagami\Nand the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when we decided to investigate together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:26.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be completed in\Njust a few more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:28.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:32.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It has twenty-three floors\Nabove the ground and two below.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's built so you can't see it\Nfrom the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:37.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are two helicopters\Non the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:38.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:39.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:43.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like all of you to spend\Nas much time here as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:45.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the number of investigators\Nincreases on this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:48.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we can accommodate\Nabout sixty people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa shouldn't have any complaints\Nif we give her, her own floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:55.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really amazing...\Nbut to go to these lengths...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:59.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Ryuzaki, where's the money\Nto pay for this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:04.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I want to solve this case,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:05.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... you didn't answer the question...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mass murders are bad enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:15.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't forgive the one who\Nput my dad and me through all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:18.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to solve this no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then become intimate with Misa\Nand investigate her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that. That's inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:33.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just feel very motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:35.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, Chief Yagami, Light,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,let's all try to catch Kira,\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:39.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:42.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...\NBut you didn't include me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:57.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we're all here.\NThen let's begin our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To further the growth\Nof the Yotsuba Group...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:03.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and for our company to become\Nthe biggest business in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:06.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who shall we kill-?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:10.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough to kill someone every week...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:16.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be irrelevant,\Nbut why has Kira begun killing like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:19.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, haven't you already noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:20.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:24.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the most advantageous\Ncourse of action for Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Advantageous?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:29.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that Kira has began\Na killing service is advantageous, Higuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:32.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:34.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be killed\Nif you're too stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:38.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The eight of us here are still young,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but we're all aiming to land\Nin the CEO's chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:45.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And since we started these meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:48.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,our salaries have been raised well\Nabove the other employees'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:52.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of odd that Kira would\Nback a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:54.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:58.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of us has to be Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:11.20,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(391,254)}Takeshi Ooi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:11.20,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(109,255)}Eiichi Takahashi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:11.20,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(109,479)}Masahiko Kida
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:11.20,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(259,206)}Kyosuke Higuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:11.20,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(535,204)}Reiji Namikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:11.20,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(539,438)}Suguru Shimura
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:11.20,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,437)}Shingo Mido
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:11.20,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(395,478)}Arayoshi Hatori
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:07.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,85)}So, back to business.\NDoes anyone have a proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,85)}Who should we have Kira kill\Nto further our interests?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:18.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,are disgusting creatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:28.40,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:33.78,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:42.79,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:49.20,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:53.76,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:59.48,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:06.92,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:12.12,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:22.86,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:28.67,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:37.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.02,0:22:42.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk like you want me to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.62,0:22:45.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around, Ryuzaki!
